title: Best Of (Lamar beats Brady on TNF, Dak says he's focused on wins not stats, What did LeBron’s cryptic post mean?)
description:
00:00 Brady and Bucs lose to Lamar and Ravens 27-22 on TNF
12:19 The duo briefly discuss their World Series predictions. Dak says he wants the Cowboys to win and is not worried about personal stats
24:36 LeBron makes cryptic Instagram post with Lakers still searching for first win
